Class QLFrameData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.eyetechds.quicklink.QLFrameData

  • public class QLFrameData
extends java.lang.Object
    The QLFrameData class defines the complete data that is available for each frame.
    See Also:
    QLDevice.getFrame(int), QLImageData, QLEyeData, QLWeightedGazePoint, QLDevice
